Positive_Review:
Great hotel with staff who cares about your stay and tries to make it better each day;
The facilities are excellent: the bedroom with the sea view is spacious and well decorated; the breakfast has many options and it's delicious. There is a station where you can make your own Vietnamese coffee; The swimming pool is big enough to swim in a relaxing environment. The staff at both bars are friendly and the service is very good.
We also rented a bike through the hotel and it only took 10 minutes to arrive.

Good location - next to beach;
very helpful staff;
Excellent room and facilities;
Good breakfast.
